============
Installation
============

Grab the latest version of id3ren from http://cbothamy.free.fr/projects/id3ren

Unpack it :

% tar xzvf id3ren-Version.tgz

Install it :

% cd id3ren-Version
% su
% make install

id3ren gets installed in /usr/bin.
Man page gets installed in /usr/man

